## Build output
[Bb]in/
[Oo]bj/
[Dd]ebug/
[Rr]elease/
x64/
x86/

## Visual Studio
.vs/
*.user
*.suo
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates

## Rider
.idea/

## Generated interop assemblies (regenerate per machine)
lib/Interop.SolidEdge*.dll

## Runtime logs and API dumps (generated locally per SE installation)
logs/
*.log
src/**/logs/

## Keep the typed typelib dump as the offline SDK reference
!src/**/logs/SE_API_dump_*.txt

## Solid Edge / CAD files generated during tests
*.par
*.asm
*.psm
*.dft
*.cfg

## Except intentional test fixtures
!scripts/*.par
!scripts/*.asm
!scripts/*.cfg

## Temporary / output files
output/
electrodes/
reports/
*.tmp
*.cache

## OS files
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
.DS_Store
